** Patch Ubuntu 20.04 Server

#sudo apt
#sudo apt list --upgrade                          
#sudo apt upgrade
                This will upgrade the packages listed out on the apt list – upgrade output.
                To omit a package for whatever reason just place package on hold, see instructions below.
 
** Hold package for upgrade.

#sudo apt-mark hold <package to hold>
#sudo apt-mark showhold
#sudo apt-mark unhold <package you held>
#sudo apt upgrade

** Update specific package

#sudo apt –-only-upgrade install <package name>

** Clean up space
#sudo apt autoremove
#sudo apt autoclean
